        "description": {
            "value": "<p>The touch of undeath runs through your blood. Your family tree might contain powerful undead, like a vampire, or perhaps you died and returned a bit different.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell List</strong> divine</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Intimidation, Religion</p>\n<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong> cantrip <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Chill Touch]</em>, 1st: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Harm]</em>, 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.False Life]</em>, 3rd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Bind Undead]</em>, 4th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Talking Corpse]</em>, 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Cloudkill]</em>, 6th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Vampiric Exsanguination]</em>, 7th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Finger of Death]</em>, 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Horrid Wilting]</em>, 9th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Wail of the Banshee]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Undeath's Blessing]</em>, advanced: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Drain Life]</em>, greater: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Grasping Grave]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magic</strong> Necromantic energy flows through you or one target. Either you gain temporary Hit Points equal to the spell's level for 1 round, or a target takes 1 negative damage per spell level (if the spell already deals initial negative damage, combine this with the spell's initial damage before determining weaknesses and resistances).</p>"
        },
